{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "DOP/clothbodycollider", "tags": "cloth"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Surface Collider"], "extent": [43, 64]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Create a Static Object from SOP Geometry pre-configured for interaction with cloth."], "extent": [64, 156]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [156, 171], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is used for a static object that influences a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/clothobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Cloth Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/clothobject"}, ". It is similar to the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/rigidcollider", "type": "link", "text": ["Volume Collider"], "fullpath": "/shelf/rigidcollider"}, ", the main difference being that the Surface Collider interacts with polygons and the Volume Collider interacts with volumes. "], "extent": [171, 452]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["You should use a Surface Collider if your static object is moving around and colliding with cloth, such as for the body of a character interacting with clothing. You should use a ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/rigidcollider", "type": "link", "text": ["Volume Collider"], "fullpath": "/shelf/rigidcollider"}, " if your object is not deforming, for example for a terrain that a cloth object is interacting with."], "extent": [452, 771]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Surface Collider"], "extent": [771, 800], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry to convert to a static object."], "extent": [800, 863]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/clothbodycollider", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/clothbodycollider"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/staticobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Surface Collider"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/staticobject"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Cloth"]}, " or ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Solid"]}, " tab."], "extent": [863, 989]}], "container": true}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 4, "text": [" "], "role": "item", "extent": [989, 1000], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["You can ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/handles", "type": "link", "text": ["transform, rotate, scale"], "fullpath": "/basics/handles"}, ", and ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/anim/basics", "type": "link", "text": ["keyframe"], "fullpath": "/anim/basics"}, " the static object at various frames."], "extent": [1000, 1127]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1127, 1136], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/clothobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Cloth Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/clothobject"}], "extent": [1136, 1178]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject"}], "extent": [1178, 1216]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/staticsolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Static Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/staticsolver"}], "extent": [1216, 1260]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/groundplane", "type": "link", "text": ["Ground Plane"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/groundplane"}], "extent": [1260, 1302]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/terrainobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Terrain 